@wp.kernel
def expr_rythfk(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = float(0.0)
    v2 = float(1.0)
    tmp = float(0.0)
    v1 = ((0.13 / (v1 + 0.22 + v2 + 0.84)) + v0)
    v0 = (v1 * wp.cos((v2 + 0.96 * tmp + 0.87)))
    tmp = tmp
    v2 = ((wp.abs(v0 + 0.17) * (tmp + 0.12 - tmp + 0.76)) / v1)
    v2 = ((0.37 * v2) / (wp.abs(v2 + 0.2) - wp.exp(v2 + 0.1)))
    tmp = wp.cos(0.21)
    data[tid] = v0
